import {Link} from 'react-router-dom'

import context from '../../context/ModeContext'

import {
  EachVideo,
  ThumbnailImage,
  DetailsCard,
  Description,
  ProfileLogo,
  ChannelName,
  PublishedAt,
  Views,
  Title,
  Paragraph,
} from './styledComponents'

const VideoCard = props => {
  const {videoData} = props

  const {
    channelName,
    id,
    profileImageUrl,
    publishedAt,
    thumbnailUrl,
    title,
    viewCount,
  } = videoData

  return (
    <Link to={id}>
      <EachVideo>
        <ThumbnailImage src={thumbnailUrl} alt={title} />
        <DetailsCard>
          <ProfileLogo src={profileImageUrl} alt="profile" />
          <Description>
            <Title>{title}</Title>
            <Paragraph>
              <ChannelName>{channelName}</ChannelName>
              <Views>Views {viewCount}</Views>
              <PublishedAt>{publishedAt}</PublishedAt>
            </Paragraph>
          </Description>
        </DetailsCard>
      </EachVideo>
    </Link>
  )
}
export default VideoCard
